	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><strong>No Action Cost </strong>- 1 Creature - Permanent - 3/Long Rest</p><p><em>Trigger: You use @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.cPayfG1ZskRXod73]{Life Tap}.</em></p><p>You target the same creature, potentially making your Life Tap permanent.</p><p><strong>Charisma Save</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target takes 3d8 necrotic damage and is &amp;reference[cursed]{Cursed}. While cursed in this way, the target cannot gain temporary hit points or regain lost hit points.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> Target takes 3d8 necrotic damage, no other effect.</p></li></ul>",
